271
00:30:58,592 --> 00:31:03,773
[SPEAKER_00]: If the parents don't choose to be involved, that's fine, but we need their voice.

272
00:31:04,053 --> 00:31:13,035
[SPEAKER_00]: We need parents to have an outlet to get involved, committees to look at all kinds of things that are going on in our school, both positive and negative.

273
00:31:13,575 --> 00:31:17,856
[SPEAKER_00]: So that's briefly the things that I find extremely important.

