279
00:32:22,204 --> 00:32:40,235
[SPEAKER_01]: I'm wondering, and maybe I'm entirely wrong, but I'm wondering if there's anything that we can do under our purview to make the school committee a place that's more inviting to our citizenry.

280
00:32:40,255 --> 00:32:46,219
[SPEAKER_01]: Because right now I don't think the general public feels like it's a very inviting place to be.

281
00:32:47,847 --> 00:33:01,920
[SPEAKER_04]: Yes, but I caution to say that of course one of the biggest ways that citizens show how they're feeling about their elected members is the elections which took place and just, you know, reelected all the members.

282
00:33:06,005 --> 00:33:12,427
