00:35:25,516 --> 00:35:28,518
[SPEAKER_06]: I think we've been trying to interview the superintendent.

312
00:35:28,938 --> 00:35:31,059
[SPEAKER_06]: And I am very frustrated by that.

313
00:35:31,119 --> 00:35:36,743
[SPEAKER_06]: I've called, I've emailed, I've done several things, and I have not been able to get a response

